---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import chevron from "../assets/imgs/icons/chevron-right.svg";
import mapPin from "../assets/imgs/icons/map-marker-outline.svg";
import externalLink from "../assets/imgs/icons/open-in-new.svg";
import clarkTower from "../assets/imgs/ClarkTower.png";
import parkingGarage from "../assets/imgs/ParkingGarage.png";
import "../assets/stylesheets/shapes.css";
import "../styles/global.css";

const pageInfo = {
  title: "Contact Us - Mind Matters Memphis",
  description:
    "Contact information and driving directions for our boutique neuropsychology office in Memphis, TN.",
};
---

<Layout page={pageInfo}>
  <div class="text-accessbody">
    <div class="bg-dust text-midnight text-xl pt-8 sm:p-8 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div
        class="contact-parallelogram bg-sand h-40 sm:h-50 md:h-64 flex flex-col justify-center justify-self-center mx-4 sm:mx-12 shadow-2xl"
      >
        <span class="visually-hidden">
          A decorative parallelogram element, sand color, framing the header
          content.
        </span>
        <h1
          class="text-midnight text-5xl sm:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-accessdisplay font-bold uppercase text-center flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
        >
          Contact
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-9">
        <div
          class="hidden md:col-span-2 md:flex justify-end items-center mr-[12%]"
        >
          <div class="contact-chevron bg-inlet h-0 md:h-44 lg:h-56">
            <span class="visually-hidden">
              A decorative chevron element, big sky blue color, pointing right
              to the contact information (phone and email).
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sm:px-8 md:col-span-6 xl:col-span-5 flex flex-col">
          <p class="p-8 pt-0">
            To request a neuropsychology appointment or evaluation from Dr.
            Amanda Gould at Mind Matters Memphis, please contact us via one of
            the following methods:
          </p>
          <div class="sm:w-fit self-center p-2 pl-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 sm:w-fit">
              <div class="pl-2 flex gap-2 items-center">
                <img src={chevron.src} alt=">" class="text-coral h-8 w-8" />
                <h2>Phone:</h2>
              </div>
              <a href="tel:+19017667500" class="underline"> 901-766-7500 </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 p-2 sm:w-fit">
              <div class="pl-2 flex gap-2 items-center">
                <img src={chevron.src} alt=">" class="text-coral h-8 w-8" />
                <h2>Email:</h2>
              </div>
              <a href="mailto:info@mindmattersmemphis.com" class="underline">
                info@mindmattersmemphis.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-dust grid md:grid-cols-4 xl:grid-cols-6">
      <div
        class="grid justify-center md:col-start-1 md:col-span-3 xl:col-start-2"
      >
        <div
          class="text-midnight bg-dust grid gap-4 justify-center relative text-xl py-8 sm:p-8 md:gap-8 md:max-w-[700px] md:py-16"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-center font-accessdisplay font-bold uppercase"
          >
            Referrals
          </h2>
          <p class="px-8">
            We welcome referrals from medical professionals for patients with
            epilepsy, traumatic brain injury, stroke, neurovascular accidents,
            non-epileptic seizures, and pre-surgical evaluations.
          </p>
          <p class="px-8">
            Please complete the referral form and fax it - along with patient
            records - to 901-766-7550.
          </p>
          <button
            class="bg-dust/80 font-bold font-accessbold sm:text-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 sm:px-12 border-2 border-midnight w-fit h-fit justify-self-center rounded-lg transition-all ease-in-out duration-200 relative shadow-md before:absolute before:bottom-[27.5%] before:left-[50%] before:h-[3px] before:w-0 before:origin-center before:rounded-sm before:bg-coral before:transition-all before:duration-300 before:ease-in-out before:content-[''] sm:hover:before:left-[13%] sm:hover:before:w-[74%] active:left-[1px] active:top-[2px] active:shadow-none"
          >
            Download Referral Form
          </button>
          <p class="hidden sm:block px-4 text-center">
            For questions about referrals, please email{" "}
            <a href="mailto:referrals@mindmattersmemphis.com" class="underline">
              referrals@mindmattersmemphis.com
            </a>
          </p>
          <div class="p-1 w-fit mx-auto sm:hidden text-center">
            <p>Questions about referrals?</p>
            <p>Please send us an email:</p>
            <a href="mailto:referrals@mindmattersmemphis.com" class="underline">
              referrals@mindmattersmemphis.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="hidden md:col-start-4 md:col-span-1 md:flex justify-start items-center xl:col-start-5"
      >
        <div
          class="contact-chevron rotate-180 bg-sage h-0 md:h-56 lg:h-72 -mt-32"
        >
          <span class="visually-hidden">
            A decorative chevron element, sage green color, pointing left to the
            referral information.
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-dust text-xl text-midnight py-8">
      <div
        class="contact-ribbon font-bold font-accessbold text-4xl text-dust bg-inlet flex p-4 pl-0 sm:pl-4 justify-center w-[95%] md:w-[90%]"
      >
        <div class="sm:pl-[2.5%] md:pl-[5%] flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
          <img
            src={mapPin.src}
            class="h-10 w-10 md:h-16 md:w-16 text-dust"
            alt="Map Pin icon"
          />
          <span class="visually-hidden">
            A map pin icon, white color on the blue background, indicating
            office location section.
          </span>
          <h2
            class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl text-center font-accessdisplay font-bold uppercase pt-1 sm:pt-2"
          >
            Office Location
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 max-w-[500px] sm:pt-8">
          <p class="">
            Mind Matters Memphis is located in Clark Tower at 5100 Poplar
            Avenue,
            <span class="font-bold font-accessbold"> Suite 322</span>, on the{
              " "
            }
            <span class="font-bold font-accessbold">3rd floor</span>.
          </p>
          <p class="">
            The Clark Tower at 5100 Poplar Ave. is the tallest building on the
            North side of Poplar, between White Station and Mendenhall.
          </p>
          <div class="block sm:flex justify-center items-center">
            <div
              class="flex items-center justify-center pt-2 sm:pt-0 gap-2 sm:gap-4 md:gap-6"
            >
              {
                /* <MapPin class="h-12 w-12 text-coral">
                <span class="visually-hidden">
                  A map pin icon, coral color, highlighting neighboring Google
                  Maps link to office location.
                </span>
              </MapPin> */
              }
              <a
                href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/xzPcNcK3tTgqiAFS9"
                class=""
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                <button
                  class="flex gap-4 items-center p-4 px-8 border-2 border-inlet rounded-lg font-bold font-accessbold"
                >
                  <span>Get Directions</span>
                  <img
                    src={externalLink.src}
                    class="h-8 w-8 text-inlet"
                    alt="External link icon"
                  />
                  <span class="visually-hidden">
                    An external link icon, coral color, indicating the link
                    opens in a new tab.
                  </span>
                </button>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid items-center p-4 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-accessdisplay text-center p-4 lg:pb-12">
              Parking Options
            </h2>
            <ul class="py-4 max-w-[500px]">
              <li class="py-2 lg:pb-12">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-accessbold">
                  1. Ground Level Outside
                </h4>
                <p>
                  If you park outside on the ground level, there are two “banks”
                  of elevators in the lobby. Take the right bank, which goes to
                  the lower floors.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li class="py-2 lg:pt-12">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-accessbold">
                  2. Parking Garage
                </h4>
                <p>
                  {
                    `If you park in the garage (which is often easier), enter the parking
                garage on the West side, bearing left to go to the upper part of
                Level 3. You'll see a sign for the entrance to Tower Room, and glass
                doors leading to the 3rd floor (our floor). You may park in any
                space labeled for guests.`
                  }
                </p>
                <p class="pt-4">
                  When entering the third floor from the parking garage, our
                  suite is at the end of the first hallway to the left.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center italic font-accessitalic">
            <div>
              <img
                src={clarkTower.src}
                alt="Aerial view of Clark Tower, with west side parking garage entrance indicated."
              />
              <p class="py-2">Clark Tower, note parking garage entrance</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img
                src={parkingGarage.src}
                alt="Entrance to Clark Tower level 3 from parking garage."
              />
              <p class="py-2">
                Entrance to Clark Tower level 3 from parking garage
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
